Post Factory (Link User)
database/factories/PostFactory.php

use App\Models\User;

return [
    'user_id' => User::factory(),
    'title' => fake()->sentence(),
];

Seeder (Large Dataset)
User::factory()
    ->count(50)
    ->hasPosts(20)
    ->create();


ğŸ”¥ Creates:

50 users

1000 posts

PART 4ï¸âƒ£ â€” CONDITIONAL STATES (VERY IMPORTANT ğŸ”¥)
Define States in Factory
public function published()
{
    return $this->state([
        'status' => 'published',
    ]);
}

Use State in Seeder
Post::factory()->count(100)->published()->create();

